@malmalmal:

For the most part you should be fine.  There are quite a few diferences, however, that may throw you for a loop.

Wikipedia has a decent summary of some of the differences: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spanish_language

Here's another summary of some of the differences: http://spanish.about.com/cs/historyofspanish/f/varieties.htm

Having said that, there are currently no cracks to get level 4 and 5 working.  So, you won't be able to use them right now anyways.
